      <h1>Data Deletion</h1>
      <p class="last-updated">Last updated: March 6, 2026</p>

      <section>
        <h2>Request Data Deletion</h2>
        <p>
          If you would like us to delete any personal data we have collected about you, including data from Instagram interactions, newsletter subscriptions, or any other communication, you can request deletion by following the steps below.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>How to Request Deletion</h2>
        <ol>
          <li>Send an email to <a href="mailto:sunkissed.hills@gmail.com">sunkissed.hills@gmail.com</a> with the subject line <strong>"Data Deletion Request"</strong>.</li>
          <li>Include the email address or social media handle associated with the data you want deleted.</li>
          <li>We will process your request and confirm deletion within 30 days.</li>
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>What Gets Deleted</h2>
        <p>Upon request, we will delete:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Your email address from our newsletter or contact lists</li>
          <li>Any messages or personal information you've sent us</li>
          <li>Any data collected through Instagram or other social media integrations</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Please note that we cannot delete data held by third-party platforms (e.g., Instagram, Spotify). To delete your data from those services, please contact them directly.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Questions?</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about data deletion, please contact us at <a href="mailto:sunkissed.hills@gmail.com">sunkissed.hills@gmail.com</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
          For more details on how we handle your data, see our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
